  "body": "This is a minor feature request that the `truffle init` command take an optional string parameter which for this demonstration I'll call `myProjectName`. The command would be a shortcut that if the optional parameter is present, runs the following three commands: \r\n\r\n`mkdir <myProjectName>`  \r\n`cd <myProjectName>`\r\n`truffle init`\r\n\r\nThe idea is just to make that introductory process a little smoother.",
